{"tid":1587471,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［無可疑］12歲男童海邊 摸蜆 後 「遇溺不治」","createTime":"2019-09-22T11:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T15:11:16.000Z","uid":226548,"like":5,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"31f830368c59a251606bfcb9936b9cb1ddc29f71","tid":1587471,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:53:00.000Z","msg":"2019-09-22 HKT 00:38<br />\n<br />\n一名12歲男童在大埔龍尾對開海面遇溺死亡。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨日下午接報，指<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">該名少年摸蜆期間，懷疑遇溺後失蹤。</span></strong>警方連同消防及飛行服務隊到場搜救，消防救起該名少年，他當時昏迷，被送往那打素醫院後，證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方初步調查相信<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">事件無可疑</span></strong>，有待驗屍確定死因。"},{"pid":"0a4a179217e77387c631ec29644b3293f24ceeb3","tid":1587471,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:53:29.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1481854-20190922.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1481854-20190922.htm&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBu2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=360dfdc9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1481854-20190922.htm&h=6586f982\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1481854-20190922.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e4821e218e313d4b51faf88a8f45065f135cef3b","tid":1587471,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a57d7dd1ba844b08521516b05d75229dddbd74c","tid":1587471,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c2c604176adab959028b5961571c3f1d002e2511","tid":1587471,"uid":114226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco